quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  8,61,"Ariko nibahitamo inzira y’amahoro, na we uzayigane kandi wiringire Allah. Mu by’ukuri ni We Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  8,62,"Kandi nibashaka kukuryarya, mu by’ukuri, Allah araguhagije. Ni We waguteye inkunga y’ubutabazi bwe n’iy’abemeramana"
  8,63,"(Allah) yanahuje imitima yabo (nyuma y’uko bari batatanye). N’iyo wari gutanga ibiri mu isi byose, ntiwari gushobora guhuza imitima yabo (abemeramana). Ariko Allah yarayihuje. Mu by’ukuri We ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  8,64,Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Allah n’abemeramana bagukurikiye baraguhagije
  8,65,"Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Shishikariza abemeramana kwitabira urugamba. Muri mwe, nihabamo makumyabiri bihangana, bazatsinda magana abiri. Kandi nihabamo ijana, bazatsinda igihumbi muri ba bandi bahakanye, kubera ko ari abantu badasobanukiwe"
  8,66,"Ubu noneho Allah araborohereje, kandi azi ko mwifitemo intege nke. Bityo muri mwe nihabamo ijana bihangana, bazatsinda magana abiri. Kandi nihabamo igihumbi bazatsinda ibihumbi bibiri ku bushake bwa Allah. Rwose Allah ari kumwe n'abihangana"
  8,67,"Ntibikwiye ko umuhanuzi yagira imfungwa z’intambara, keretse amaze kwizera ko yatsinze urugamba. Murashaka indonke z’isi (muhabwa incungu kuri izo mfungwa zo ku rugamba rw’ i Bad’ri), kandi Allah ashaka (ko mubona ingororano) z’imperuka. Rwose, Allah ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  8,68,"Iyo bitaza kuba itegeko rya Allah ryabanje (ribemerera iminyago no kugira imfungwa z’intambara), mwari kugerwaho n’ibihano bihambaye kubera ibyo mwakiriye (incungu)"
  8,69,"Ngaho nimurye mu minyago mwafashe, iziruwe kandi myiza. Munatinye Allah; mu by'ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe"
  8,70,"Yewe Muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Bwira imfungwa z’intambara ziri mu maboko yanyu uti “Niba Allah azi ko hari icyiza kiri mu mitima yanyu, azabaha ibyiza biruta ibyo mwanyazwe, anabababarire ibyaha byanyu. Rwose, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe.”"
  8,71,"Ariko nibashaka kuguhemukira (nyuma yo kubarekura), rwose (ntuzacike intege) kuko na mbere bahemukiye Allah (bakurwanya) maze aguha imbaraga zo kubatsinda. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  8,72,"Mu by'ukuri ba bandi bemeye bakanimuka (bimukira i Madina), bagaharanira inzira ya Allah bakoresheje imitungo yabo n’imbaraga zabo, ndetse na ba bandi babakiriye bakanabarwanaho; abo (abimukira n’ababakiriye) ni inshuti hagati yabo. Naho ba bandi bemeye ariko ntibimuke, si ngombwa kubagira inshuti kugeza bimutse. Ariko kandi nibabitabaza ku mpamvu z’idini, mujye mubatabara, keretse (mu gihe abo barwana na bo) ari abantu mufitanye amasezerano (yo kudaterana). Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  8,73,"Na ba bandi bahakanye ni inshuti hagati yabo. Nimutabigenza mutyo (ngo namwe mukundane), hazaba ingorane n'ubwangizi bukomeye ku isi"
  8,74,"Naho ba bandi bemeye bakanimukira (i Madina), bagaharanira inzira ya Allah, ndetse na ba bandi babakiriye bakanabarwanaho; abo ni bo bemera by’ukuri. Bazababarirwa ibyaha banahabwe amafunguro meza"
  8,75,"Na ba bandi baje kwemera nyuma, nuko bakanimuka (bimukira i Madina), bakanifatanya namwe mu guharanira inzira ya Allah, abo bari muri mwe. Ariko abafitanye amasano, bamwe bafite uburenganzira busumba ubw’abandi (mu izungura) rishingiye ku mategeko ya Allah. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umumenyi wa byose"